@startuml
title Диаграмма классов модуля управления ядром (Parakeet)

class ParakeetCLI {
    - config: Config
    - configurator: KernelConfigurator
    - builder: KernelBuilder
    - installer: KernelInstaller
    + run(): void
}

class Config {
    - data: dict
    + load(path: str): Config
    + get_flash_devices(): list
    + get_kernel_params(): dict
    + get(key: str, default: any): any
}

class KernelConfigurator {
    + configure(linux_dir: str, backup_dir: str): bool
    - backup_config(src: str, dst_dir: str): void
}

class KernelBuilder {
    + build(linux_dir: str, jobs: int): bool
    - is_built(): bool
}

class KernelInstaller {
    - temp_dir: str
    + install(config: Config, devices: list): bool
    - prepare_temp_dir(): str
    - install_modules(): void
}

class BootDevice {
    - device: str
    - partition: str
    - mountpoint: str
    + mount(): void
    + umount(): void
    + copy_kernel_files(temp_dir: str): void
    + update_grub(): void
    + install_grub(): void
}

class Logger {
    - log_file: str
    + info(msg: str): void
    + error(msg: str): void
    + command(cmd: list): void
}

ParakeetCLI --> Config : uses
ParakeetCLI --> KernelConfigurator : uses
ParakeetCLI --> KernelBuilder : uses
ParakeetCLI --> KernelInstaller : uses
KernelInstaller --> BootDevice : creates and manages (1..*)
ParakeetCLI ..> Logger : uses
KernelConfigurator ..> Logger : uses
KernelBuilder ..> Logger : uses
KernelInstaller ..> Logger : uses
BootDevice ..> Logger : uses
@enduml
